  <sys:String x:Key="DescLabel">There are [i]many[/i] ways to implement localization in [style=ColoredText]NoesisGUI[/style]. In this example we are using our [style=ColoredText][i]Loc[/i][/style] markup extension, which references resources in a local [i]ResourceDictionary[/i]. The desired language dictionary is selected in the root [i]DataContext[/i]. The [style=ColoredText][i]RichText[/i][/style] attached property for [i]TextBlocks[/i] allows you to use BBCode markup in your text. It supports text formatting, images, and bindings to the [i]DataContext[/i] (e.g. the music level is [style=ColoredNumber][bind format='{0:0}%']MusicLevel[/bind][/style]).</sys:String>

